comments: Turner (IND) cleanly blocks Tatum's (BOS) driving shot attempt.
Tatum (BOS) slightly extends his arm on the gather as he changes directions.
Sabonis (IND) establishes himself in a legal picking position in Walker's (BOS) path and does not deliver any contact.
Theis (BOS) makes contact with Oladipo's (IND) arm during his driving shot attempt.
Theis (BOS) establishes himself in a legal screening position in Warren's (IND) path.
Warren (IND) makes marginal contact with Tatum (BOS) at the start of his drive and doesn't affect his SQBR.
Hayward (BOS) legally contest Turner's (BOS) jump shot.
Smart (BOS) releases from Sabonis (IND) at the end of his drive and does not extend his off-arm.
Smart (BOS) gathers the ball on his right foot and takes two legal steps prior to his release.
Sabonis (IND) is not in a vertical position as he continues to move into Smart's (BOS) space and delivers contact that affects his driving shot attempt.
While Walker (BOS) is in a legal defensive position alongside Oladipo (IND), Oladipo's foot makes incidental contact with Walker's leg.
Smart (BOS) is in the lane for longer than three seconds without actively guarding an opponent.
Sabonis (IND) establishes himself in Walker's (BOS) path during the pick and makes marginal contact.
Walker (BOS) legally contest Oladipo's (BOS) jump shot.
Oladipo (IND) commits a take foul on Walker (BOS).
Holiday (IND) commits a take foul on Walker (BOS).
Sabonis (IND) slightly extends his arms as he releases from the pick, but the contact is marginal.
Tatum (BOS) jumps toward the basket to contest the shot and absorbs the contact initiated by Oladipo (IND).
Smart (BOS) is not established in Holiday's (IND) path when he delivers contact during the off-ball screen.
Sabonis (IND) commits a take foul on Smart (BOS).
Walker (BOS) removes his hand as Holiday (IND) enters his upward motion and legally contests the jump shot attempt.
Oladipo (IND) engages and disengages with Smart (BOS) during the rebound.
